45
00:04:08,924 --> 00:04:11,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

46
00:04:11,524 --> 00:04:13,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll say this to all of you.</b></font>

47
00:04:13,794 --> 00:04:18,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm aware that even if we do this,
it could all be for nothing.</b></font>

48
00:04:18,804 --> 00:04:23,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But D has made it this far
with a perfect record of victory,</b></font>

49
00:04:23,504 --> 00:04:29,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and I can't sit back while my stupidity
causes the loss that breaks that record.</b></font>

50
00:04:29,714 --> 00:04:33,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if it costs me my life, I <i>will</i> race!</b></font>

51
00:04:43,564 --> 00:04:46,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please pick up the pace in small increments.</b></font>

52
00:04:46,334 --> 00:04:48,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't try to push it too far.</b></font>

53
00:04:48,964 --> 00:04:50,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

54
00:04:50,304 --> 00:04:54,674
