56
00:04:56,974 --> 00:04:58,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, got it.</b></font>

57
00:04:58,514 --> 00:05:00,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Here goes.</b></font>

58
00:05:11,484 --> 00:05:15,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm counting on you, FD!</i></b></font>

59
00:05:15,264 --> 00:05:19,434
