<i>without sleep to make this happen...</i></b></font>

60
00:05:19,434 --> 00:05:21,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And for my own pride...</i></b></font>

61
00:05:21,864 --> 00:05:24,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's pull off a miracle!</i></b></font>

62
00:05:28,544 --> 00:05:31,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Them idiots all turned white as sheets!</b></font>

63
00:05:31,504 --> 00:05:36,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Especially that spiky-haired bastard
in the FD. He was shakin' like a leaf!</b></font>

64
00:05:36,744 --> 00:05:41,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those guys talk a lotta crap, but they just
can't bring it. What a bunch of losers!</b></font>

65
00:05:41,684 --> 00:05:47,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we can scare that other driver in the
Eight-Six as well, we win both races!</b></font>

66
00:05:47,454 --> 00:05:49,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ducks in a barrel, man!</b></font>

67
