68
00:06:10,244 --> 00:06:12,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but it looks like I can pull off left-side cornering.</i></b></font>

69
00:06:12,914 --> 00:06:14,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The problem is the right!</i></b></font>

70
00:06:14,984 --> 00:06:20,154
