<i>balance of load to the front,</i></b></font>

75
00:06:54,354 --> 00:06:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>it suddenly spun out.</i></b></font>

76
00:06:57,294 --> 00:07:00,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I thought that with a little more work we</i>
<i>could turn this around somehow, but...</i></b></font>

77
00:07:00,334 --> 00:07:02,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...I was naive!</i></b></font>

78
00:07:04,364 --> 00:07:09,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What should I do? I can't</i>
<i>face the others like this.</i></b></font>

79
00:07:12,874 --> 00:07:18,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Brother... I'm sorry. I just want to cry.</i></b></font>

80
00:07:27,554 --> 00:07:30,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no. Someone's coming.</b></font>

81
00:07:30,864 --> 00:07:34,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute. That's the
sound of a rotary engine.</b></font>

82
00:07:48,344 --> 00:07:54,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hi! I came to cheer you on again.
What are you doing out here?</b></font>

83
00:07:56,754 --> 00:07:58,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um...</b></font>

84
00:07:59,824 --> 00:08:04,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is my darling mad at me?</i>
<i>Am I being too persistent?</i></b></font>

85
00:08:07,564 --> 00:08:10,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please listen. I...</b></font>

86
00:08:10,864 --> 00:08:12,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to ask a favor!</b></font>

87
00:08:14,704 --> 00:08:18,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Reduce Speed"</b></font>

88
00:08:16,604 --> 00:08:18,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since the days of the Red Suns,</b></font>

89
00:08:18,714 --> 00:08:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's been an unwritten rule
that we only race our own cars.</b></font>

90
00:08:24,014 --> 00:08:28,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'm breaking that rule!
Let me do this, brother!</b></font>

91
00:08:28,054 --> 00:08:31,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't approve, I still intend to race.</b></font>

92
00:08:31,724 --> 00:08:35,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't even have to be
an official Project D race.</b></font>

93
00:08:35,094 --> 00:08:39,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me race! No... I have to race!</b></font>

94
00:08:51,604 --> 00:08:54,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello? It's Ryosuke.</b></font>

95
00:08:54,074 --> 00:08:58,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry for the short notice, but I
won't be needing that car after all.</b></font>

96
00:08:58,914 --> 00:09:04,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. That's right. Sorry. I'll call you again later.</b></font>

97
00:09:04,954 --> 00:09:10,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Brother... Wait, were you trying
to get another car ready?</b></font>

98
00:09:10,724 --> 00:09:18,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not a very elegant solution, I thought,
but there was no other alternative.</b></font>

99
00:09:18,804 --> 00:09:23,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The last thing I wanted to do was
concede defeat without having even run...</b></font>

100
00:09:23,744 --> 00:09:26,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Especially to those whom we face this time.</b></font>

101
00:09:26,944 --> 00:09:29,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah!</b></font>

102
00:09:29,784 --> 00:09:34,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Ryosuke, will they accept a change of cars?</b></font>

103
00:09:34,784 --> 00:09:39,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll gladly push rules on us to
put the advantage in their favor,</b></font>

104
00:09:39,324 --> 00:09:44,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I bet they'll raise hell over anything
that gives us the least bit of an edge.</b></font>

105
00:09:44,124 --> 00:09:47,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have reason to believe they'll allow it.</b></font>

106
00:09:47,534 --> 00:09:51,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be forceful with them, and be defiant.</b></font>

107
00:09:51,104 --> 00:09:53,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It will probably work.</b></font>

108
00:09:53,704 --> 00:09:59,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! I don't care if it's the
same model, it's still a different car!</b></font>

109
00:09:59,044 --> 00:10:02,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Screw that! I ain't gonna allow it!</b></font>

110
00:10:02,214 --> 00:10:06,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh. I thought you said we could
"use the Eight-Six or somethin',"</b></font>

111
00:10:06,784 --> 00:10:08,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as I recall.</b></font>

112
00:10:08,824 --> 00:10:12,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit. I didn't say nothin' like that!</b></font>

113
00:10:12,624 --> 00:10:16,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>F1 rules allow a "T car"
for use as a backup, yes?</b></font>

114
00:10:16,494 --> 00:10:19,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So let's cut to the chase.</b></font>

115
00:10:19,494 --> 00:10:22,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'd be using a borrowed car
we've never driven before.</b></font>

116
00:10:22,564 --> 00:10:25,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The odds are overwhelmingly
in your favor, correct?</b></font>

117
00:10:27,834 --> 00:10:35,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't allow this, our only option
is to say that Project D was never here.</b></font>

118
00:10:36,744 --> 00:10:41,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can take both cars and head back
to Gunma. Is that what you want?</b></font>

119
00:10:46,254 --> 00:10:50,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Talk about a surprise. Just like you said,
I was forceful with them and it worked.</b></font>

120
00:10:50,994 --> 00:10:54,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Meaning there's more to
this than meets the eye.</b></font>

121
00:10:54,394 --> 00:10:58,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For all their complaining about what
an inconvenience it is to race us,</b></font>

122
00:10:58,434 --> 00:11:02,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>they're strangely adamant about
what constitutes a victory for them.</b></font>

123
00:11:02,344 --> 00:11:05,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's something we can't overlook.</b></font>

124
00:11:05,774 --> 00:11:09,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There must be a reason
they're so determined to win.</b></font>

125
00:11:09,614 --> 00:11:15,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And not for victory's sake,
but for something more tangible.</b></font>

126
00:11:15,214 --> 00:11:18,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't tell me... Money?!</b></font>

127
00:11:18,854 --> 00:11:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It could be.</b></font>

128
00:11:20,624 --> 00:11:25,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hearing that makes me that much more
determined not to lose to those guys!</b></font>

129
00:11:33,874 --> 00:11:36,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How pitiful.</b></font>

130
00:11:36,874 --> 00:11:40,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wantin' to win so bad you'd
wheel out someone else's car...</b></font>

131
00:11:40,314 --> 00:11:44,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a disgrace. These guys got no pride!</b></font>

132
00:11:44,784 --> 00:11:49,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't let them provoke you, Keisuke.
If you get in a fight with them, we lose.</b></font>

133
00:11:49,224 --> 00:11:50,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I know.</b></font>

134
00:11:50,824 --> 00:11:55,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm just happy to be here at the starting line.</b></font>

135
00:11:55,124 --> 00:12:00,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Compared to that, I could care less
about their idiot attempts to provoke me.</b></font>

136
00:12:02,964 --> 00:12:06,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm grateful. To everyone...</i></b></font>

137
00:12:06,974 --> 00:12:08,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even to him.</i></b></font>

138
00:12:08,774 --> 00:12:13,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, here we go! Starting in five seconds!</b></font>

139
00:12:13,614 --> 00:12:15,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four! Three!</b></font>

140
00:12:15,984 --> 00:12:18,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two! One!</b></font>

141
00:12:18,284 --> 00:12:19,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

142
00:12:28,524 --> 00:12:33,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll tear ahead of 'im while he's still</i>
<i>tryin' to get used to an unfamiliar car.</i></b></font>

143
00:12:33,034 --> 00:12:35,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's why I chose to go</i>
<i>in front for the first race.</i></b></font>

144
00:12:35,864 --> 00:12:40,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I ain't no fool! I'm gonna win this for sure!</i></b></font>

145
00:12:48,614 --> 00:12:52,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Ryosuke, there's
something I want to ask you.</b></font>

146
00:12:52,354 --> 00:12:55,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't expect you to cancel
the car you were preparing</b></font>

147
00:12:55,014 --> 00:12:57,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and let Keisuke use the other one.</b></font>

148
00:12:57,884 --> 00:13:02,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like you, that way of thinking.</b></font>

149
00:13:02,364 --> 00:13:05,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've misunderstood slightly.</b></font>

150
00:13:05,364 --> 00:13:07,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If either were to be driven for the first time,</b></font>

151
00:13:07,394 --> 00:13:11,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I chose the one that would be
slightly less of a burden for Keisuke.</b></font>

152
00:13:11,704 --> 00:13:14,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you understand?</b></font>

153
00:13:14,204 --> 00:13:18,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh! Keisuke had raced against that car once!</b></font>

154
00:13:18,344 --> 00:13:20,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Correct.</b></font>

155
00:13:20,074 --> 00:13:23,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He had seen up close how it
performed at maximum levels,</b></font>

156
00:13:23,644 --> 00:13:28,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and is probably aware on a sensory level
of how it is different from his own FD.</b></font>

157
00:13:28,854 --> 00:13:33,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To me, it was the only choice that
would prove advantageous in battle.</b></font>

158
00:13:33,754 --> 00:13:37,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There were no romantic
concerns at all in my decision.</b></font>

159
00:13:37,924 --> 00:13:41,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That girl's coming here tonight...</b></font>

160
00:13:41,534 --> 00:13:45,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...was the greatest luck that
Keisuke could have asked for.</b></font>

161
00:13:51,374 --> 00:13:56,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>As I thought, this car's got power and</i>
<i>the underbody carries itself smoothly.</i></b></font>

162
00:13:56,784 --> 00:14:00,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Thank you. This is a good car!</i></b></font>

163
00:14:02,554 --> 00:14:05,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, this was a bit of a shock.</b></font>

164
00:14:05,054 --> 00:14:08,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoko, letting someone
borrow your FD for a race...</b></font>

165
00:14:08,594 --> 00:14:10,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll forgive me for saying it like this,</b></font>

166
00:14:10,394 --> 00:14:14,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you've had a sort of
unnatural affection for that car.</b></font>

167
00:14:14,564 --> 00:14:16,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's strange even to me.</b></font>

168
00:14:16,804 --> 00:14:23,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I always hated the idea of letting
anyone but me drive my car...</b></font>

169
00:14:23,204 --> 00:14:30,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I didn't hate it, I was really happy.
I've never felt this way before!</b></font>

170
00:14:30,144 --> 00:14:36,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If my FD can help my darling,</i>
<i>then I'll gladly let him use it.</i></b></font>

171
00:14:36,924 --> 00:14:41,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sure enough, my darling is special to me.</i></b></font>

172
00:14:41,324 --> 00:14:43,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Win, my darling!</i></b></font>

173
00:15:01,144 --> 00:15:04,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Awesome! That was perfect slide control!</b></font>

174
00:15:04,644 --> 00:15:11,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a borrowed FD, right? Sure enough,
Keisuke Takahashi is an FD specialist!</b></font>

175
00:15:11,124 --> 00:15:15,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, there's a bit of space
between them. This looks rough.</b></font>

176
00:15:15,424 --> 00:15:20,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Apparently they couldn't practice
running this course at all last night.</b></font>

177
00:15:20,034 --> 00:15:22,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But they still agreed to go
up against a Lancer Evo?!</b></font>

178
00:15:22,534 --> 00:15:25,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This race could be a dangerous one for them!</b></font>

179
00:15:32,044 --> 00:15:36,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Some journalist wrote in some magazine...</i></b></font>

180
00:15:36,284 --> 00:15:40,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>When it comes to general street racing,</i>
<i>the Lancer Evo is the fastest in the world!</i></b></font>

181
00:15:40,884 --> 00:15:44,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Some stupid FD doesn't stand a chance!</i></b></font>

182
00:15:50,624 --> 00:15:54,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I ain't got time to be playin' around, boy.</i>
<i>Just disappear already!</i></b></font>

183
00:15:59,074 --> 00:16:04,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been thinking... I think what will
make this race is extremely simple.</b></font>

184
00:16:04,674 --> 00:16:08,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke has two major handicaps.</b></font>

185
00:16:08,574 --> 00:16:11,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first is that he's not in his own car.</b></font>

186
00:16:11,184 --> 00:16:14,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The second is, he hasn't practiced this course.</b></font>

187
00:16:14,914 --> 00:16:18,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Normally, this would be a
completely unwinnable race,</b></font>

188
00:16:18,754 --> 00:16:23,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but with enough of a difference in the
drivers' abilities, the handicap is lessened.</b></font>

189
00:16:23,324 --> 00:16:27,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's skills are far
superior to his opponent's.</b></font>

190
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:30,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know that, do you?</b></font>

191
00:16:30,234 --> 00:16:33,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just instinct, but if I
saw it, I'd know for sure.</b></font>

192
00:16:33,234 --> 00:16:35,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not that good a driver.</b></font>

193
00:16:35,574 --> 00:16:40,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Under normal conditions, I think
Keisuke would've already won by now.</b></font>

194
00:16:40,374 --> 00:16:42,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

195
00:16:42,014 --> 00:16:46,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because of the handicap, right now
there's a kind of balance between them...</b></font>

196
00:16:46,284 --> 00:16:50,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what kind of race the hillclimb is.</b></font>

197
00:16:59,134 --> 00:17:01,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't shake him. Why?!</i></b></font>

198
00:17:20,414 --> 00:17:23,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is ridiculous. This is a Lancer Evo!</i></b></font>

199
00:17:23,984 --> 00:17:26,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My foot's so far on the gas that</i>
<i>I'm takin' corners so fast and scary</i></b></font>

200
00:17:26,754 --> 00:17:29,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that I gotta keep my eyes</i>
<i>from poppin' outta my head,</i></b></font>

201
00:17:29,664 --> 00:17:34,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so how can some guy who hasn't even</i>
<i>practiced this course be keepin' up?!</i></b></font>

202
00:17:34,564 --> 00:17:38,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Pick up the pace, idiot!</i>
<i>You're gonna make that Lancer Evo cry!</i></b></font>

203
00:18:06,164 --> 00:18:11,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He takes winding corners the orthodox way,</i>
<i>on a line that goes toward the center.</i></b></font>

204
00:18:11,204 --> 00:18:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I take corners tighter, close to the in-line.</i></b></font>

205
00:18:14,434 --> 00:18:18,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Lancer Evo pulls ahead</i>
<i>where the line's a bit tough for me,</i></b></font>

206
00:18:18,344 --> 00:18:23,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but at the next left, I'll take a wide</i>
<i>line and pick up cornering speed.</i></b></font>

207
00:18:23,384 --> 00:18:27,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Then I'll tear ahead of him on</i>
<i>the course's longest straightaway!</i></b></font>

208
00:18:29,054 --> 00:18:31,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll use the cornering tactic I used</i>
<i>in Tochigi against the R34,</i></b></font>

209
00:18:31,224 --> 00:18:34,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>where speeding as you come</i>
<i>out of the corner entry is key.</i></b></font>

210
00:18:34,324 --> 00:18:39,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Against a high-speed, 4WD Lancer Evo,</i>
<i>it will be make-or-break time!</i></b></font>

211
00:18:45,234 --> 00:18:48,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You stupid son of a bitch!</i>
<i>Don't you know? Up ahead,</i></b></font>

212
00:18:48,504 --> 00:18:52,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>there's a construction barricade</i>
<i>that makes the road narrower!</i></b></font>

213
00:18:52,374 --> 00:18:55,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There ain't enough room for</i>
<i>two cars to go side by side!</i></b></font>

214
00:18:59,714 --> 00:19:04,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't come any closer!
I ain't got enough space!</b></font>

215
00:19:07,494 --> 00:19:09,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You dumb son of a bitch!</b></font>

216
00:19:09,424 --> 00:19:11,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What the hell?</i></b></font>

217
00:19:28,514 --> 00:19:30,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, asshole!</b></font>

218
00:19:30,414 --> 00:19:34,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You suck! This is Project D?</b></font>

219
00:19:34,014 --> 00:19:38,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This</i> is how you do things?
Hog the road like a damn maniac?!</b></font>

220
00:19:38,524 --> 00:19:42,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I hadn't pulled back,
that would've been a huge accident!</b></font>

221
00:19:42,964 --> 00:19:45,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You really think that?</b></font>

222
00:19:45,934 --> 00:19:47,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

223
00:19:47,294 --> 00:19:49,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just don't take in
your surroundings, do you?</b></font>

224
00:19:49,634 --> 00:19:51,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What'd you say?</b></font>

225
00:19:51,104 --> 00:19:56,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you'd gone far enough over to the right,
both cars could've passed side by side.</b></font>

226
00:19:56,044 --> 00:20:01,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you couldn't instantly see that,
you don't know what you're talking about.</b></font>

227
00:20:01,874 --> 00:20:06,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This wasn't some winding,
G-shaped curve. It was a straightaway!</b></font>

228
00:20:06,984 --> 00:20:10,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd planned on going two centimeters
toward the left barricade,</b></font>

229
00:20:10,124 --> 00:20:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which would've opened up about five
centimeters for you along the guardrail.</b></font>

230
00:20:15,494 --> 00:20:17,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Quit talkin' crap!</b></font>

231
00:20:17,824 --> 00:20:22,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just don't get it. Not with
that amount of driving instinct.</b></font>

232
00:20:22,064 --> 00:20:27,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That you couldn't adapt on the fly,
changing course to come in at full speed...</b></font>

233
00:20:27,904 --> 00:20:30,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's really disappointing.</b></font>

234
00:20:30,074 --> 00:20:37,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After that, the real battle should've been how
we execute braking techniques at top speed.</b></font>

235
00:20:39,454 --> 00:20:42,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Those</i> are the kinds of
races I've run up till now.</b></font>

236
00:20:42,184 --> 00:20:45,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got nothing else to say to your ass.</b></font>

237
00:20:48,324 --> 00:20:49,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>True to form, eh?</b></font>

238
00:20:49,594 --> 00:20:51,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

239
00:20:57,364 --> 00:20:59,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

240
00:20:59,304 --> 00:21:01,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a good car.</b></font>

241
00:21:12,684 --> 00:21:16,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way we can deny
this one. We had witnesses.</b></font>

242
00:21:16,524 --> 00:21:18,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit!</b></font>

243
00:21:18,124 --> 00:21:22,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I didn't expect him to lose on the hillclimb.</i></b></font>

244
00:21:22,224 --> 00:21:27,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The next opponent is that kid. Whatever.</i></b></font>

245
00:21:36,644 --> 00:21:40,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Lancer Evo's got a rear wing, huh?</b></font>

246
00:21:40,174 --> 00:21:42,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How many Evos does this make now?</b></font>

247
00:21:42,984 --> 00:21:46,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Six. They make for tough races.</b></font>

248
00:21:46,254 --> 00:21:50,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's somethin' I wanna
say before we get started.</b></font>

249
00:21:50,424 --> 00:21:53,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're pretty young. What's your name?</b></font>

250
00:21:53,824 --> 00:21:55,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara.</b></font>

251
00:21:55,254 --> 00:22:04,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, Fujiwara. This is just between us,
but all you guys are sorta in trouble.</b></font>

252
00:22:04,564 --> 00:22:09,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That guy that lost the race
just now has sort of flipped out.</b></font>

253
00:22:09,174 --> 00:22:12,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's called up a bunch of his friends,
really bad characters.</b></font>

254
00:22:12,674 --> 00:22:17,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a lot of them, and they
should be on their way right now.</b></font>

255
00:22:17,214 --> 00:22:23,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>C'mon, don't look at me like that.
I don't like stuff like that, either.</b></font>

256
00:22:23,284 --> 00:22:26,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you seem like an all right guy,
so I thought I'd give you a heads-up.</b></font>

257
00:22:26,624 --> 00:22:31,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd be best if you sorta didn't race too hard.</b></font>

258
00:22:31,364 --> 00:22:38,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In exchange, I can cover for ya...
make sure you at least don't get hurt.</b></font>

259
00:22:38,264 --> 00:22:40,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, in other words...</b></font>

260
00:22:40,634 --> 00:22:43,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're telling me to lose on purpose?</b></font>

261
00:22:43,074 --> 00:22:48,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nah, I didn't say that.
All I said was not to race too hard.</b></font>

262
00:22:48,074 --> 00:22:53,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sayin' this to be kind. Think about it.</b></font>

263
00:22:59,494 --> 00:23:04,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable. <i>Somebody</i> blew a
race that should've been easy as hell,</b></font>

264
00:23:04,164 --> 00:23:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so now it's up to me.</b></font>

265
00:23:08,964 --> 00:23:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm gonna have to win at least one of these.</i>
<i>I've already gone and planted the seeds...</i></b></font>

266
00:23:16,744 --> 00:23:23,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it, Fujiwara? You're looking
more serious than usual. You nervous?</b></font>

267
00:23:23,244 --> 00:23:26,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Matsumoto. The truth is, just now...</b></font>

268
00:23:28,784 --> 00:23:30,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He said that, did he?</b></font>

269
00:23:30,654 --> 00:23:32,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. What do you think about it?</b></font>

270
00:23:32,954 --> 00:23:37,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't. Who's gonna buy
a cheap threat like that?</b></font>

271
00:23:37,694 --> 00:23:42,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Forget everything that doesn't matter.
Just concentrate on the race.</b></font>

272
00:23:42,364 --> 00:23:47,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The only reason we're even here is to win!</b></font>

273
00:23:47,104 --> 00:23:50,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. I was thinking the same thing.</b></font>

274
00:23:50,274 --> 00:23:53,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, here we go!</b></font>

275
00:23:53,814 --> 00:23:56,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Starting in five seconds!</b></font>

276
00:23:56,184 --> 00:23:58,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four! Three!</b></font>

277
00:23:58,184 --> 00:24:00,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two! One!</b></font>

278
00:24:00,814 --> 00:24:02,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

279
00:24:18,964 --> 00:24:26,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I gave no advice to Keisuke or Fujiwara.</i>
<i>This time, I will have them act freely.</i></b></font>

280
00:24:26,844 --> 00:24:32,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The driver of the Evo VI is</i>
<i>more skilled than I thought.</i></b></font>

281
00:24:32,144 --> 00:24:34,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>While he appears nondescript at first glance,</i></b></font>

282
00:24:34,414 --> 00:24:37,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>on the downhill, that is likely</i>
